Comment: 0,0:02:15.06,0:02:16.23,Default,Machi,0,0,0,,Huh?
Comment: 0,0:00:04.28,0:00:06.58,Default,Machi,0,0,0,,Mr. Takahashi, um...
Comment: 0,0:00:06.58,0:00:08.43,Default,Machi,0,0,0,,Thank you for your help the other day.
Comment: 0,0:00:08.43,0:00:11.47,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,O-Oh, no problem.
Comment: 0,0:00:11.47,0:00:13.15,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,Is your cold better now?
Comment: 0,0:00:13.15,0:00:16.90,Default,Machi,0,0,0,,Yes, thank you. I'm all better.
Comment: 0,0:00:16.90,0:00:18.03,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,Oh, good.
Comment: 0,0:00:18.93,0:00:20.14,Default,Machi,0,0,0,,Mr. Takahashi?
Comment: 0,0:00:20.14,0:00:23.11,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,Er, sorry. I was just...
Comment: 0,0:00:24.01,0:00:26.53,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,Thinking about what an odd sight this is.
Comment: 0,0:02:00.79,0:02:02.54,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,{\i1}Machi Kyouko.
Comment: 0,0:02:02.54,0:02:04.37,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,{\i1}She's a dullahan,
Comment: 0,0:02:04.98,0:02:08.52,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,{\i1}an Irish demi, whose legend is rooted in fairies,
Comment: 0,0:02:08.52,0:02:10.89,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,{\i1}and whose head and body are separate.
Comment: 0,0:02:11.36,0:02:15.06,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,Is it safe to touch the flame \Ncoming from your neck?
Comment: 0,0:02:16.23,0:02:17.72,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,Is it hot?
Comment: 0,0:02:17.72,0:02:20.65,Default,Machi,0,0,0,,N-No... Would you like to touch it?
Comment: 0,0:02:22.50,0:02:25.19,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,You're right. It doesn't feel hot at all.
Comment: 0,0:02:25.19,0:02:27.44,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,It's more like grabbing air.
Comment: 0,0:02:27.44,0:02:30.74,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,Feels strange, like something out of this world.
Comment: 0,0:02:32.45,0:02:34.38,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,Wh-What's wrong?
Comment: 0,0:02:34.38,0:02:37.72,Default,Machi,0,0,0,,Touching it puts pressure on my nerves.
Comment: 0,0:02:37.72,0:02:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It's very uncomfortable!
Comment: 0,0:02:39.01,0:02:42.36,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,S-Sorry... If you just tell me, I'll understand. {wtf}
Comment: 0,0:02:42.36,0:02:44.52,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,Your body isn't a separate being, right?
Comment: 0,0:02:44.52,0:02:46.62,Default,Machi,0,0,0,,No, it's just my body.
Comment: 0,0:02:46.62,0:02:50.78,Default,Machi,0,0,0,,See? See? See?
Comment: 0,0:02:49.96,0:02:51.82,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,{\3c&H1E1D47&}Whoa, it is true!
Comment: 0,0:02:50.78,0:02:52.97,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,See?
Comment: 0,0:02:53.85,0:02:55.44,Default,Machi,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Comment: 0,0:02:55.44,0:02:57.53,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,Nothing. Uh...
Comment: 0,0:02:57.53,0:02:59.44,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,By the way, when you collapsed,
Comment: 0,0:02:59.85,0:03:03.68,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,was it all right to carry your head and body separately?
Comment: 0,0:03:03.68,0:03:04.68,Default,Machi,0,0,0,,Yes.
Comment: 0,0:03:04.68,0:03:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,They've been as far apart \Nas Tokyo and Okayama.
Comment: 0,0:03:08.25,0:03:10.53,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,Okayama?! That's really far!
Comment: 0,0:03:10.53,0:03:12.24,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,What happened?
Comment: 0,0:03:12.24,0:03:16.91,Default,Machi,0,0,0,,My grandparents live in Okayama, so I visit them every year.
Comment: 0,0:03:16.91,0:03:19.37,Default,Machi,0,0,0,,But saying goodbye on the train platform was so hard,
Comment: 0,0:03:19.95,0:03:23.46,Default,Machi,0,0,0,,my body took off without my head.
Comment: 0,0:03:23.46,0:03:25.13,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,I see...
Comment: 0,0:03:26.87,0:03:28.87,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,This is pretty crazy.
Comment: 0,0:03:28.87,0:03:31.30,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,I'm sure it must be troublesome in your daily life.
Comment: 0,0:03:31.72,0:03:36.25,Default,Machi,0,0,0,,I work through those issues with my family, using trial and error.
Comment: 0,0:03:36.25,0:03:38.32,Default,Machi,0,0,0,,It's all about experience and ingenuity!
Comment: 0,0:03:38.32,0:03:39.16,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,Ah...
Comment: 0,0:03:39.16,0:03:41.71,Default,Machi,0,0,0,,For instance, when I eat,
Comment: 0,0:03:41.71,0:03:44.24,Default,Machi,0,0,0,,I hold it in place, like this.
Comment: 0,0:03:44.24,0:03:45.93,Default,Machi,0,0,0,,When I use the bath or toilet,
Comment: 0,0:03:45.93,0:03:48.32,Default,Machi,0,0,0,,I hang it like this, so there's no problem.
Comment: 0,0:03:48.82,0:03:50.92,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,This is very informative...
Comment: 0,0:03:50.92,0:03:55.37,Default,Machi,0,0,0,,Thankfully, I'm able to handle most things on my own.
Comment: 0,0:03:55.37,0:03:58.90,Default,Machi,0,0,0,,But, my biggest struggle, is interacting with others.
Comment: 0,0:03:58.90,0:03:59.66,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,Interacting?
Comment: 0,0:04:00.10,0:04:04.73,Default,Machi,0,0,0,,Yes, when people see me for the first time, they're startled.
Comment: 0,0:04:04.73,0:04:07.56,Default,Machi,0,0,0,,So getting comfortable with one another takes time.
Comment: 0,0:04:07.56,0:04:09.47,Default,Machi,0,0,0,,Especially at this time of year...
Comment: 0,0:04:09.47,0:04:11.43,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,Right, since you just joined this school.
Comment: 0,0:04:11.43,0:04:15.24,Default,Machi,0,0,0,,I got sick and missed the entrance ceremony.
Comment: 0,0:04:15.24,0:04:18.11,Default,Machi,0,0,0,,Then I missed three days.
Comment: 0,0:04:18.11,0:04:20.93,Default,Machi,0,0,0,,I forced myself to come to school,
Comment: 0,0:04:20.93,0:04:23.49,Default,Machi,0,0,0,,but I ended up collapsing.
Comment: 0,0:04:23.49,0:04:25.94,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,No wonder I hadn't seen you around.
Comment: 0,0:04:25.94,0:04:28.69,Default,Machi,0,0,0,,Hikari{-chan} is different,
Comment: 0,0:04:28.69,0:04:32.67,Default,Machi,0,0,0,,but I feel like there's some distance between my classmates and me.
Comment: 0,0:04:32.67,0:04:35.39,Default,Machi,0,0,0,,It's not like we don't talk,
Comment: 0,0:04:36.09,0:04:39.91,Default,Machi,0,0,0,,but they seem to avoid anything related to dullahans.
Comment: 0,0:04:40.69,0:04:45.25,Default,Machi,0,0,0,,I would feel better if I could joke with them
Comment: 0,0:04:45.25,0:04:47.27,Default,,0,0,0,,about my dullahan aspects.
Comment: 0,0:04:47.27,0:04:48.09,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,I see...
Comment: 0,0:04:51.69,0:04:52.49,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,Machi.
Comment: 0,0:04:52.49,0:04:53.17,Default,Machi,0,0,0,,Y-Yes?
Comment: 0,0:04:53.81,0:04:56.39,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,Do you ever make jokes like that yourself?
Comment: 0,0:04:56.39,0:04:59.04,Default,Machi,0,0,0,,Huh? No, I don't.
Comment: 0,0:04:59.04,0:05:00.22,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,You don't?
Comment: 0,0:05:00.22,0:05:03.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, maybe that's where you should start.
Comment: 0,0:05:03.66,0:05:04.65,Default,Machi,0,0,0,,I should?
Comment: 0,0:05:05.01,0:05:07.11,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,If that's the sort of friendship you want,
Comment: 0,0:05:07.11,0:05:10.00,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,you should tell some jokes to set a tone,
Comment: 0,0:05:10.00,0:05:13.23,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,so they'll know what kinds of jokes you can share with them.
Comment: 0,0:05:14.14,0:05:16.80,Default,Machi,0,0,0,,I see. Jokes, huh?
Comment: 0,0:05:16.80,0:05:21.47,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,In short, it's all about who takes the first step.
Comment: 0,0:05:21.47,0:05:25.61,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,Thinking of it that way, \Nyour classmates have the higher hurdle to clear.
Comment: 0,0:05:25.61,0:05:27.29,Default,Machi,0,0,0,,Right, since I'm a dullahan!
Comment: 0,0:05:29.12,0:05:33.03,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,You're probably the first real, live dullahan they've seen...
Comment: 0,0:05:33.03,0:05:35.30,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,Aren't there only three in the whole world?
Comment: 0,0:05:35.72,0:05:38.14,Default,Machi,0,0,0,,Huh? Yes, that's right.
Comment: 0,0:05:38.14,0:05:39.31,Default,Machi,0,0,0,,I'm surprised you know that.
Comment: 0,0:05:39.76,0:05:42.04,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,Well, I've done my research.
Comment: 0,0:05:42.04,0:05:43.94,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,All for my precious students.
Comment: 0,0:05:46.63,0:05:49.31,Default,Machi,0,0,0,,Mr. Takahashi, um...
Comment: 0,0:05:50.31,0:05:51.65,Default,Machi,0,0,0,,W-Well...
Comment: 0,0:05:51.65,0:05:56.71,Default,Machi,0,0,0,,If you don't want to, feel free to decline, but...
Comment: 0,0:05:57.22,0:05:58.75,Default,Machi,0,0,0,,Um...
Comment: 0,0:06:01.91,0:06:05.51,Default,Machi,0,0,0,,W-Would you please hug me?!
Comment: 0,0:06:13.86,0:06:15.26,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,Was that a joke?
Comment: 0,0:06:15.26,0:06:18.24,Default,Machi,0,0,0,,No... Only my head.
Comment: 0,0:06:18.24,0:06:19.05,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,Your head?
Comment: 0,0:06:23.14,0:06:24.31,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,Like this?
Comment: 0,0:06:24.31,0:06:26.73,Default,Machi,0,0,0,,Y-Yes! Exactly like that...
Comment: 0,0:06:27.21,0:06:29.85,Default,Machi,0,0,0,,I... I enjoy being held like this,
Comment: 0,0:06:29.85,0:06:32.23,Default,Machi,0,0,0,,and my parents often used to do it.
Comment: 0,0:06:32.72,0:06:37.24,Default,Machi,0,0,0,,But now that I'm in high school, they told me to get over it.
Comment: 0,0:06:37.24,0:06:39.66,Default,Machi,0,0,0,,But I just can't,
Comment: 0,0:06:39.66,0:06:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,and there's no one else I can ask...
Comment: 0,0:06:42.79,0:06:43.87,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,Okay.
Comment: 0,0:06:44.62,0:06:48.52,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,{\i1}Alone, a dullahan's head can't do anything.
Comment: 0,0:06:49.21,0:06:50.51,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,{\i1}To get around,
Comment: 0,0:06:50.51,0:06:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}it needs contact with others, even if that's its own body.
Comment: 0,0:06:54.08,0:06:59.10,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,{\i1}In other words, hating solitude is part of a dullahan's nature.
Comment: 0,0:06:59.10,0:07:01.89,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,{\i1}Put another way, they get lonely easily.
Comment: 0,0:07:01.89,0:07:05.22,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,{\i1}This little dullahan still wants to be coddled.
Comment: 0,0:07:06.63,0:07:08.27,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,But you know,
Comment: 0,0:07:08.27,0:07:11.99,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,considering that I'm a teacher, \Nthis might look inappropriate.
Comment: 0,0:07:11.99,0:07:13.40,Default,Machi,0,0,0,,R-Really?
Comment: 0,0:07:13.84,0:07:17.88,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,Well, as long as no troublesome \Npests see us, it should be fine.
Comment: 0,0:07:17.88,0:07:20.09,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,Like stubborn higher-ups
Comment: 0,0:07:20.09,0:07:23.53,Default,,0,0,0,,or that chatty vampire...
Comment: 0,0:07:23.91,0:07:28.83,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,700)}Or anyone... like that...
Comment: 0,0:07:34.63,0:07:36.77,Default,Hikari,0,0,0,,Everyone!
Comment: 0,0:07:36.77,0:07:39.47,Default,Hikari,0,0,0,,Check this out!
Comment: 0,0:07:42.65,0:07:46.43,Default,Machi,0,0,0,,I guess this means you're one of the dullahans now.
Comment: 0,0:07:46.43,0:07:47.05,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,Eh?
Comment: 0,0:07:47.05,0:07:50.02,Default,Machi,0,0,0,,Because your head's going to roll, right?
Comment: 0,0:07:50.02,0:07:53.73,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,That's a joke I can't laugh at!
Comment: 0,0:07:53.73,0:07:55.33,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,Wait! Hikari!
Comment: 0,0:07:56.25,0:07:57.95,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,Wait, wait, wait!
Comment: 0,0:07:58.94,0:08:00.40,Default,Machi,0,0,0,,Thanks, Hikari{-chan}.
Comment: 0,0:08:01.61,0:08:02.49,Default,Hikari,0,0,0,,For what?
Comment: 0,0:08:02.49,0:08:06.91,Default,Machi,0,0,0,,I'm really glad I was able to talk to Mr. Takahashi{-sensei}.
Comment: 0,0:08:08.09,0:08:13.06,Default,Hikari,0,0,0,,Oh, just seeing that panicked look on his face was enough for me!
Comment: 0,0:08:16.25,0:08:17.25,Default,Hikari,0,0,0,,Yukki!
Comment: 0,0:08:17.81,0:08:19.61,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,Takanashi{-san}...
Comment: 0,0:08:19.61,0:08:23.18,Default,Hikari,0,0,0,,Ah, you're so cold! This feels great!
Comment: 0,0:08:24.28,0:08:26.21,Default,Hikari,0,0,0,,Your home is this way, too?
Comment: 0,0:08:26.21,0:08:26.60,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Comment: 0,0:08:27.00,0:08:29.00,Default,Hikari,0,0,0,,Then, let's walk home together!
Comment: 0,0:08:29.00,0:08:30.86,Default,Hikari,0,0,0,,Oh, this is Macchi.
Comment: 0,0:08:31.68,0:08:33.31,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,Macchi?
Comment: 0,0:08:37.54,0:08:39.66,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,I need to stop somewhere on the way.
Comment: 0,0:08:40.28,0:08:43.60,Default,Hikari,0,0,0,,Really? Can't be helped, I guess...
Comment: 0,0:08:43.60,0:08:46.40,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,I'm really sorry. Bye.
Comment: 0,0:08:47.87,0:08:49.45,Default,Hikari,0,0,0,,Bye-bye!
Comment: 0,0:08:49.96,0:08:53.36,Default,Machi,0,0,0,,Isn't that Kusakabe{-san}, from class A?
Comment: 0,0:08:53.36,0:08:54.53,Default,Machi,0,0,0,,The snow woman?
Comment: 0,0:08:54.53,0:08:55.94,Default,Hikari,0,0,0,,Yep, that's Yukki.
Comment: 0,0:08:55.94,0:08:58.95,Default,Hikari,0,0,0,,She's a little shy, but she's nice.
Comment: 0,0:08:58.95,0:09:00.01,Default,Machi,0,0,0,,Oh...
Comment: 0,0:09:00.45,0:09:02.69,Default,Hikari,0,0,0,,And her body is so cold!
Comment: 0,0:09:02.69,0:09:04.85,Default,,0,0,0,,She feels so nice to hug!
Comment: 0,0:09:04.85,0:09:07.30,Default,Machi,0,0,0,,Oh, so that's why you suddenly hugged her like that.
Comment: 0,0:09:12.44,0:09:15.02,Default,Hikari,0,0,0,,My house is that way. Wanna stop by?
Comment: 0,0:09:15.02,0:09:18.73,Default,Machi,0,0,0,,Hmm... It's already pretty late.
Comment: 0,0:09:18.73,0:09:20.52,Default,Hikari,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's true.
Comment: 0,0:09:20.52,0:09:22.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet your parents would worry.
Comment: 0,0:09:22.79,0:09:25.74,Default,Hikari,0,0,0,,Well, come over again when you have time to visit.
Comment: 0,0:09:25.74,0:09:26.64,Default,Machi,0,0,0,,Sure.
