Comment: 0,0:20:23.69,0:20:27.26,Default,Hikari,0,0,0,,Yeah, I really freaked out that one time, though!
Comment: 0,0:20:27.26,0:20:28.72,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,That one time?
Comment: 0,0:20:28.72,0:20:30.20,Default,Machi,0,0,0,,Nothing! It's nothing!
Comment: 0,0:20:30.20,0:20:33.78,Default,Machi,0,0,0,,Um, thank you for helping me with this, Mr. Takahashi!
Comment: 0,0:20:33.78,0:20:36.82,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,No, I should thank you.
Comment: 0,0:20:36.82,0:20:38.41,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,I learned a lot today.
Comment: 0,0:20:38.41,0:20:40.71,Default,Machi,0,0,0,,Then the experiment was a success.
Comment: 0,0:20:40.71,0:20:43.10,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,Yep. A great success.
Comment: 0,0:20:43.10,0:20:45.01,Default,Hikari,0,0,0,,Grmff sffsmfs!
Comment: 0,0:20:45.42,0:20:46.96,Default,Hikari,0,0,0,,Bye-bye!
Comment: 0,0:20:46.96,0:20:48.66,Default,Hikari,0,0,0,,See you later!
Comment: 0,0:20:50.81,0:20:52.19,Default,Hikari,0,0,0,,Hey, Mr. T.
Comment: 0,0:20:52.19,0:20:52.85,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,What?
Comment: 0,0:20:52.85,0:20:54.85,Default,Hikari,0,0,0,,About Macchi...
Comment: 0,0:20:56.13,0:20:57.01,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,What about her?
Comment: 0,0:20:59.81,0:21:03.81,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,Principal, dullahans have carry their heads all the time.
Comment: 0,0:21:04.32,0:21:07.52,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,And carrying a regulation bag takes up one hand.
Comment: 0,0:21:08.12,0:21:10.86,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,It's inconvenient. Worse, it's dangerous.
Comment: 0,0:21:11.72,0:21:15.82,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,For class 1-B's Machi Kyouko, couldn't you give permission
Comment: 0,0:21:15.82,0:21:18.83,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,to use a backpack instead of the regulation bag?
Comment: 0,0:21:18.83,0:21:22.16,Default,Principal,0,0,0,,That's a good point. I didn't give that enough thought.
Comment: 0,0:21:22.16,0:21:24.29,Default,Principal,0,0,0,,Of course I'll grant permission.
Comment: 0,0:21:24.29,0:21:26.50,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Comment: 0,0:21:26.50,0:21:28.47,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,I have one other favor to ask.
Comment: 0,0:21:28.47,0:21:29.62,Default,Principal,0,0,0,,What is it?
Comment: 0,0:21:29.62,0:21:32.09,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,We should also consider her \Nhomeroom teacher's position.
Comment: 0,0:21:32.09,0:21:35.59,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,So could we just say this was your order?
Comment: 0,0:21:37.31,0:21:39.58,Default,Principal,0,0,0,,{\fad(1,500)}I see. Very well.
Comment: 0,0:21:40.96,0:21:42.27,Default,Hikari,0,0,0,,Morning, Mr. T!
Comment: 0,0:21:42.27,0:21:44.30,Default,Machi,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Comment: 0,0:21:44.30,0:21:46.84,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,Hey. Oh, a backpack?
Comment: 0,0:21:46.84,0:21:51.79,Default,Machi,0,0,0,,Yes. Yesterday, my homeroom teacher told me I could use this instead.
Comment: 0,0:21:51.79,0:21:53.82,Default,Hikari,0,0,0,,You're looking good, Macchi!
Comment: 0,0:21:54.21,0:21:55.45,Default,Hikari,0,0,0,,Right, Mr. T?
Comment: 0,0:21:55.45,0:21:57.18,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,Yeah, it suits you.
Comment: 0,0:22:05.05,0:22:05.09,Default,chptr,0,0,0,,{ED}
Comment: 0,0:23:35.63,0:23:37.63,Default,Voice,0,0,0,,{\an8}Tập kế on {\i1}Demi-chan muốn được trò chuyện:{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:23:38.23,0:23:40.01,Default,Voice,0,0,0,,{\an8}Succubus{-san} is a Real Adult.
Comment: 0,0:23:39.70,0:23:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,
Comment: 0,0:07:39.93,0:07:43.61,Default -top,Hikari,0,0,0,,{\an8}Hey! Hey! This is big!
Comment: 0,0:07:43.61,0:07:46.43,Default -top,Hikari,0,0,0,,{\an8}Gather around, people!
Comment: 0,0:07:55.33,0:07:57.95,Default -top,Hikari,0,0,0,,{\an8}Hey, listen! Mr. Takahashi{-sensei} was...
Comment: 0,0:18:48.88,0:18:52.61,Default -top,Hikari,0,0,0,,{\an8}There we go, there we go...
Comment: 0,0:03:38.39,0:03:39.17,Default,Tetsuo,0,0,0,,Ồ...
Comment: 0,0:08:26.28,0:08:26.61,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,Ưm.
Comment: 0,0:08:58.97,0:08:59.89,Default,Machi,0,0,0,,Ồ...
Comment: 0,0:09:25.81,0:09:26.76,Default,Machi,0,0,0,,Ừm.
Comment: 0,0:12:00.38,0:12:01.27,Default,Machi,0,0,0,,Hế?
Comment: 0,0:12:17.06,0:12:17.88,Default,Hikari,0,0,0,,Ừm.
Comment: 0,0:12:36.42,0:12:37.60,Default,Hikari,0,0,0,,Ừm.
